    <DataPropertyAssertion>
        <DataProperty IRI="#description"/>
        <NamedIndividual IRI="#Goofy"/>
        <Literal datatypeIRI="&xsd;string">Goofy is the captain of the royal guard of Disney Castle and one of Sora&apos;s most faithful companions. In Kingdom Hearts II he retains his gentle, peaceful and surprisingly wise character, often more reflective than the others. He fights with a shield, which he uses both to protect his friends and to strike enemies. His absolute loyalty and pure heart make him a cornerstone of the trio.</Literal>
