    </DataPropertyAssertion>
    <DataPropertyAssertion>
        <DataProperty IRI="#description"/>
        <NamedIndividual IRI="#Roxas"/>
        <Literal datatypeIRI="&xsd;string">Roxas is characterized by a calm, introverted and reflective temperament, very different from Sora&apos;s. Despite his nature as a Nobody, he shows a strong will and a genuine desire to understand who he truly is.

Throughout the story, Roxas confronts his own identity, his bond with Sora and the fate that awaits him, becoming one of the most beloved and tragic characters in the saga.</Literal>
    </DataPropertyAssertion>
